  "bench_setup": {
    "notes": "SPI1 loopback: PA7 (MOSI, AF5) \u2192 PA6 (MISO, AF5), PA5 = SCK. Master, 8-bit, mode 0, ~62.5 kHz (APB2/256 at 16 MHz). Sends {0xA5, 0x5A, 0xF0, 0x0F, 0x12, 0x34, 0x56, 0x78}, verifies echo. PASS after all 8 bytes matched. Wire required: PA7 \u2192 PA6.",
